{"tid":2319724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［和平使者］外交部：咄咄逼人從來不是中方外交傳統","createTime":"2020-12-10T09:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T11:51:30.000Z","uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6216149b1be05198d7aed3c74824dcb21f75244b","tid":2319724,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，中國不主動惹事，但也不怕事，不會被脅迫訛詐，如果有些人因為中國面對毫無底線的攻擊、抹黑和謾罵，做出回擊，就稱為「戰狼」外交，反問為維護中國主權安全、發展利益、國家榮譽，維護國際公平與正義，做「戰狼」又何妨。 <br />\n<br />\n華春瑩回應有德國議員指中國實行「戰狼外交」時表示，中國始終堅持獨立自主的和平外交政策，咄咄逼人從來不是中方外交傳統，但卑躬屈膝也不是中國人的氣節。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩又反問，過去一段時間，中國與個別國家之間發生一些事情，哪一次由中方首先挑釁。她指出，無論是將病毒標簽化、疫情政治化、中國污名化等，質疑有人以「莫須有」罪名對中國口誅筆伐時，可以如狼似虎，而中方只能做「沈默的羔羊」。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564631-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564631-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYplQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=b6e968dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564631-20201210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0fc4eae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564631-20201210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8e70c4ab116c96dd1b56ab9ec143ecda838d658c","tid":2319724,"uid":29188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"講得啱，中國邊有傳統，朝令夕改最撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade75f255c7450b5f2ea1d2e5c8d62027961b259","tid":2319724,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"人地大選都搞埋，呢隻「沈默的羔羊」真係好沉默 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc2cc1701bb6b8836c33ebc01406b7087b36aa2","tid":2319724,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"咄咄係形容驚懼之聲<br />\n你個d係吠，當然唔係傳統"},{"pid":"c15e6e6189549f74a3a585ccb772970350e703ef","tid":2319724,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哪一次由中方首先挑釁</blockquote><br />\n每次都係"},{"pid":"2cb24f76a98555f5fc09ecfe978b6ecc5fd7c1a7","tid":2319724,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"得幾十年歷史有鳩傳統咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fa6e27c41ac36c39a499b6d29f330566dbc675","tid":2319724,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3546b51c21feb028feef4595beb5b5ad0151012","tid":2319724,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"得喇！聽到好撚悶！打未啫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3d283772543d13c091e3bb6f6c8ee7dc8f91d2","tid":2319724,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"屙緊屎忍唔住講左句屌你喇"},{"pid":"6009e5985c82c8d3955e61ddf3706ad389acfc85","tid":2319724,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e70c4ab116c96dd1b56ab9ec143ecda838d658c","tid":2319724,"uid":29188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"講得啱，中國邊有傳統，朝令夕改最撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"朝令夕改就係傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5acda7dd71d37430f52863135df6d5ab00b4014","tid":2319724,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"同一單新聞, 對內就變左咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/12/10/tlQhm5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2FtlQhm5.jpeg&h=c0d9c2f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"